d8b4e72'),(1279,9,'description7','Investments in funds investing in commercial organizations are more profitable, but also more risky. Only proven management companies participate in the Golden Visa program, and startups cannot participate.\r\nThe minimum investment amount here is 500,000€, the deposit can be returned after 5 - 7 years if you apply for citizenship.\r\n\r\nAt the moment, this is the one option that is effortless and that will make you profitable.\r\nThe qualifying funds are managed by fund managers accredited by the Portuguese Securities Market Commission (CMVM), Portugal\'s regulatory body.\r\n\r\nYou can choose from the energy, industry, and technology sectors for the Portugal Golden Visa fund investment route. Remember that the Golden Visa investment funds cannot directly or indirectly pursue real estate activities.\r\n\r\nOur manager will provide you with a list of reliable and verified funds that meet the conditions for applying for a Golden Visa and inform you about the conditions for each of them.'),(1280,9,'_description7','field_67740eddb4e73'),(1281,9,'image7','114'),(1282,9,'_image7','field_67740ee5b4e74'),(1283,109,'title','<span>Mnogodoms </span>\r\n– your trusted guide  to starting a new life in Portugal! '),(1284,109,'_title','field_6773b8da50970'),(1285,109,'description','Focus on your journey, and we’ll handle the rest'),(1286,109,'_description','field_6773b8e850971'),(1287,109,'button_text','Сontact us today'),(1288,109,'_button_text','field_6773b8f250972'),(1289,109,'button_link',''),(1290,109,'_button_link','field_6773b8fc50973'),(1291,109,'banner','28'),(1292,109,'_banner','field_6773b90250974'),(1293,109,'subtitle2','most popular'),(1294,109,'_subtitle2','field_6773bafebe855'),(1295,109,'title2','Featured properties '),(1296,109,'_title2','field_6773bb06be856'),(1297,109,'link2',''),(1298,109,'_link2','field_6773bb0abe857'),(1299,109,'properties','a:3:{i:0;s:2:\"50\";i:1;s:2:\"51\";i:2;s:2:\"43\";}'),(1300,109,'_properties','fiel